quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,18,"“Amene afuna zachangu (zosangalatsa za m’dziko ndikumaikirapo mtima pa izo), timpatsiratu mwachangu pa dziko lapansi chimene tikufuna kwa amene tafuna (kumpatsa;) koma (tsiku la chimaliziro) tamkonzera Jahannam adzailowa ali wonyozeka, wopirikitsidwa apa ndi apo"
  17,19,"“Ndipo amene afuna tsiku la chimaliziro (mzochita zake) ndikuligwilira ntchito yake yeniyeni uku ali okhulupirira, iwowo khama lawo lidzakhala lolandiridwa"
  17,20,"“Onse awa, (abwino ndi oipa), timawapatsa awa ndi awa mwazopatsa za Mbuye wako; ndipo zopatsa za Mbuye wako sizotsekerezedwa (kuti zisamfike kapolo Wake)"
  17,21,"“Taona (ndi diso lolingalira) m’mene tawasiyanitsira mkupeza bwino, ena nkukhala pamwamba pa anzawo (pa chuma ndi pa moyo wangwiro); ndipo pa tsiku la chimaliziro kusiyana kwawo pa masitepe ndi ulemelero, nkwakukulu kwabasi"
  17,22,“Usadzipangire mulungu wina ndi kumphatika kwa Allah; kuti ungadzakhale wodzudzulidwa (kwa Allah) ndikusiidwa wopanda m’thandizi
  17,23,"“Ndipo walamula Mbuye wako kuti musapembedze (wina) koma Iye Yekha, ndi kuti muchitire zabwino makolo (anu). Ngati m’modzi wa iwo afika msinkhu waukalamba uli naye, kapena onse awiri, usawanenere mawu amnyozo, ndiponso usawakalipire koma yankhula nawo ndi mau aulemu"
  17,24,"“Ndipo afungatire ndi phiko lodzichepetsa powachitira chisoni, ndipo nena: “Mbuye wanga achitireni chisoni (makolo anga) monga momwe ankandilelera ku ubwana.”"
  17,25,"“Mbuye wanu akudziwa kwambiri zomwe zili m’maganizo mwanu; ngati muli ofuna kuchita zabwino, (kwa makolo anu Iye akudziwa. Ndipo ngati mutawalakwira, kenako ndikulapa), ndithu Iye ndi Mwini kukhululukira otembenukira kwa Iye"
  17,26,"“Ndipo mnansi wako, masikini ndi wapaulendo (yemwe alibe choyendera) mpatse gawo lake (la chuma chako) ndipo usamwaze (chuma chako) mosakaza"
  17,27,"“Ndithu omwaza chuma mosakaza ndiabale a satana (otsatira satana), ndipo satana ngosathokoza kwa Mbuye wake"